Non-tradegood city trades:

	port cities buy fish
	all cities buy either clay pots or woven baskets
	plains cities sell oxen
	alchemy cities sell lead

Common (short haul) tradegoods:

	pipeweed
	ale
	tallow
	candles
	wool
	vinegar
	wax
	sugar
	salt
	glue
	linen
	beans
	walnuts
	flax
	flutes
	cassava
	plum wine

	for each region
		construct city list for region
		clear temps on local tradegoods

		for each city in region
			pick new local tradegood from list
				buy/sell it
			choose another city from the region randomly to
				sell/buy it
			set price according to distance, or fixed profit


	this algorithm requires that we have as many local tradegoods
	as there are cities in the region

	there are 39 cities in the biggest region
	but that may be somewhat atypical


